OL,3,CPlanned February transport strike
OL,4,Csuspended
OL,6,FPublic transport workers in Northern
OL,7,FIreland have called off their planned
OL,8,Fwalkout on 15 of February.
OL,10,FUnions have said the decision has been
OL,11,Ftaken to give political leaders space
OL,12,Fto make an improved pay offer.
OL,14,FThe announcement comes after after
OL,15,Fpowersharing was restored with the UK
OL,16,Fgovernment granting #3.3bn for the
OL,17,Fincoming executive a portion of which
OL,18,Fis allocated to settle public sector
OL,19,Fpay disputes.
